{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Be the protagonist of an adorable, comical and creepy fable</h2>What seemed like a colourful dream full of lovable creatures has turned into a nightmare. Help Avy escape from the island of toys by facing her greatest fears.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/extras/AvySteamGifFable02.gif?t=1725023691\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the toy island</h2>Run, jump and glide to make your way through the world of toys. Meet and play with quirky creatures and help them by completing missions.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/extras/AvySteamGifJump02.gif?t=1725023691\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solve puzzles in the shadows</h2>Push big objects, grab and throw smaller ones and interact with items in the world to solve puzzles and escape the island's dangers.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/extras/AvySteamGifDark02.gif?t=1725023691\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Engage in dialogue-based boss battles</h2>On the island, Avy will face her greatest fears. To progress in her adventure, she will have to defeat bizarre creatures in dialogue-based battles.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/extras/AvySteamGifSpider02.gif?t=1725023691\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2615870?t=1725023691","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1725023691","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725023691","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2615870/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1725023691","categories":[{"description"